category: Utils
build-depends: cygport 
sdesc: "A simple, fast and user-friendly alternative to 'find'"
ldesc: "fd is a program to find entries in your filesystem. It is a simple, fast and user-friendly alternative to find. While it does not aim to support all of find's powerful functionality, it provides sensible (opinionated) defaults for a majority of use cases."
skip:

homepage: https://github.com/sharkdp/fd
license: MIT OR Apache-2.0
